  "description": "NPS Template - Marketing template for research professionals",
  "instructions": "How to Use the NPS Template NPS Methodology Net Promoter Score measures customer loyalty on a 0-10 scale:\n\u2022 Promoters (9-10): Loyal enthusiasts who drive growth\n\u2022 Passives (7-8): Satisfied but not enthusiastic; vulnerable to competition\n\u2022 Detractors (0-6): Unhappy customers who may damage your brand Response Log Enter customer feedback here. For each response:\n1. Assign a unique Response ID\n2. Record the date and customer details\n3. Select NPS score (0-10) from dropdown\n4. The Category column auto-calculates (Promoter/Passive/Detractor)\n5. Capture verbatim feedback for analysis\n6. Track follow",
